#  O'zbek tilida
Ushbu skriptni PowerShell-da to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ishga tushirish mumkin. Biroq, bir nechta muhim qadamlarni bajarish kerak:

PowerShell-da skriptni ishga tushirish bosqichlari:
1. Skriptni yaratish va saqlash:

powershell
# Skript matnini faylga yozing
$scriptContent = @'
# (yuqoridagi to'liq skript matnini shu yerga qo'ying)
'@

# Faylni saqlash
$scriptPath = "$env:USERPROFILE\Documents\Set-LinuxAliases.ps1"
$scriptContent | Out-File -FilePath $scriptPath -Encoding UTF8
2. ExecutionPolicy ni o'zgartirish:

powershell
# Joriy foydalanuvchi uchun execution policy ni o'zgartirish
Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser -Force

# Tekshirish
Get-ExecutionPolicy -Scope CurrentUser
3. Skriptni ishga tushirish:

powershell
# To'g'ridan-to'g'ri ishga tushirish
& "$env:USERPROFILE\Documents\Set-LinuxAliases.ps1"

# Yoki
.\Documents\Set-LinuxAliases.ps1


# Ingliz tilida (English)
This script can be executed directly in PowerShell. However, several important steps must be performed:

Steps to run a script in PowerShell:
1. Create and save the script:

powershell
# Write the script content to a file
$scriptContent = @'
# (Place the full script text from above here)
'@

# Save the file
$scriptPath = "$env:USERPROFILE\Documents\Set-LinuxAliases.ps1"
$scriptContent | Out-File -FilePath $scriptPath -Encoding UTF8
2. Change the ExecutionPolicy:

powershell
# Change execution policy for the current user
Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser -Force

# Verify
Get-ExecutionPolicy -Scope CurrentUser
3. Run the script:

powershell
# Execute directly
& "$env:USERPROFILE\Documents\Set-LinuxAliases.ps1"

# Or
.\Documents\Set-LinuxAliases.ps1
